[color=#44ff00]Objective:[/color]
Harvest the necessary berries while avoiding rocks, logs, and keeping the pivot harvester on the land.

[color=#44ff00]How to play:[/color]
You control two harvesters connected by a saw. One harvester orbits the other. [color=#44ff00]Tap[/color] the screen to switch the pivot harvester. Hit mushrooms to invert the orbit.

[color=#44ff00]Tap[/color] anywhere to begin...

[color=#ff0000]You have broken your harvester![/color]

Tap anywhere to restart...

[color=#00ff00]You have successfully harvested the necessary berries![/color]

Tap anywhere to proceed...

[color=#00ff00]You have successfully harvested ALL the necessary berries![/color]

Tap anywhere to restart the game...
